<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Proofs">Proofs</h2><span cl=
ass=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a hr=
ef=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DHeron%27s_formula&amp;ac=
